  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/637",
  "title": "widget icons in /examples/ are cryptic",
  "body": "I know they are beautiful but on the /examples/ page they are raising the [FUD](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fear,_uncertainty_and_doubt).\n\nWhat do you think?\n\nI would remove them, even adding a tooltip etc won't do it I think (mobile being another reason). Too much level and quantity of information at once I feel.\n\n(I had to say it :D)\n\n![2015-11-17 14 51 59](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/11213621/314f08fc-8d3d-11e5-92a8-7f5456ab8b9e.png)\n",
